scene.message:
Nanjo: Shibuya would be far{nl}
too noisy to live in...{nl}
That one's rather out of{nl}
touch with reality.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I wanna get out of that{nl}
house soon too... It's so{nl}
embarrassing I can't even{nl}
invite friends over.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: That girl's a friend{nl}
of Yuka's.{wait_fr:16} Two of a kind,{nl}
really...{wait_fr:32} such a chatterbox.{waitkey}{ret}

Girl: I wanna live on my own{nl}
soon~ Somewhere around{nl}
Shibuya, in a cool condo~...{waitkey}{clearbox}That'd be nice, right?{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Ugh, I wanna get out of this{nl}
boring town already~{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Hey, you! This is no{nl}
time to be leisurely eating{nl}
a burger!{waitkey}{ret}
